    "The Nature Conservancy: The Nature Conservancy is a global environmental organization that works to protect and restore critical habitats, including forests.",
    "They publish regular reports on their conservation efforts, including data on biodiversity and carbon sequestration.",
    "Trees for the Future: Trees for the Future is a nonprofit organization that works with local communities to plant trees and restore degraded lands.",
